headline: CFG Bank Turns to Jack Henry to Modernize Technology and Scale Niche Services
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that CFG Bank ("CFG"), the largest bank headquartered in Baltimore, selected Jack Henry to modernize its technology infrastructure and fuel its growth trajectory.
